            int currentLevel

      • Class game.ui.LevelCompleteScreen

            int currentLevel
            The current level number that has just been completed. Used to determine if there are more levels or if the game is complete.
          • frame

          • game

            A reference to the main Game instance. This is used to facilitate level progression or trigger game completion. Provides access to methods like Game.progressToNextLevel() and Game.gameCompleted().
